==Italian==
===Etymology===
Latin ''[[ad]] + [[illiam]] + [[horam]]''

===Pronunciation===
allóra, /alˈlora/, /<tt>al"lora</tt>/
===Adverb===
'''allora'''

# [[so]]
'''''Allora''', che cosa c'è di nuovo?''
'''''So''', what's new?''
# in that time
''La bambina era '''allora''' chiamata da tutti gattina per la sua dolcezza.''
''The child was called '''in that time''' called by everybody kittie for her sweetness.''

